---
import { Container } from "../Container";
---

<section class="py-12 md:py-16">
  <Container className="flex flex-col gap-y-6 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <p class="text-base/relaxed text-gray-600 text-balance">
      Your team wiki is slow to load. Project docs are hard to organize. Quick
      notes are impossible to find later. You're constantly context-switching,
      and it's exhausting.
    </p>
    <p class="text-xl/relaxed text-gray-950 font-medium text-balance">
      Lydie unifies everything in <i>one</i> blazingly fast workspace.<br
      />Built for how you actually think and write.
    </p>
  </Container>
</section>
